<title>USA: Image Entertainment board OKs repurchase.</title>
<headline>Image Entertainment board OKs repurchase.</headline>
<dateline>CHATSWORTH, Calif. 1997-01-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Image Entertainment Inc said its board approved a 1,000,000 share increase to its existing stock repurchase plan.</p>
<p>The Board initially authorized the repurchase of 1,000,000 shares in January 1995 and in June 1996 authorized an additional 500,000 shares. The company has about 13.3 million shares outstanding.</p>
<p>Since the beginning of the program, and including recent purchases, the Company has repurchased about 1.5 million shares.</p>
